==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Preceding
<hw>Pre*ced"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Going before; --
opposed to <xex>following</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Astron.)</fld> <def>In the direction toward which
stars appear to move. See <er>Following</er>, 2.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Precel</ent>⟦br⟧
